description.en:
Harta's anthology of oneshots by assorted mangaka.

---
**Summer 2021 Contents**
1. **A Mechanic's Morning** (*Shuuriya-san no Asa*, 修理屋さんの朝) by Moryo
2. **Phantasm** (ファンタズム) by Minoru Mitsuba
3. **Hinata Impact** (日向インパクト) by Rintarou Ohshima
4. **A Naked Dream & Fulfilling Ryne** (*Zenra no Yume to Kanaeru Ryne*, 全裸の夢と叶えるライン) by Takuto Kashiki
5. **The Tale of a Streetwalker’s Lovers' Suicide** (*Yotaka Shinjuu*, 夜鷹心中) by Ameishi
6. *Shirazushirazu no Shimai* (知らず知らずの姉妹) by Yukie Nozawa
7. **The Power of Two** (*Futari no Chikara*, ふたりのチカラ) by Hiro Inuzuka
8. *Kuchibeni ga Shitai* (くちべにがしたい) by Kazuki Miura
9. *Ame to Yuuen no Machi* (雨と遊園の街) by Haruo Iwamune
10. *Gekkabijin to Tsuki no Hikari* (ゲッカビジンと月の光) by Shimu Rakuichi
11. *Senpai to Surfing to Watashi* (せんぱいとサーフィンと私) by Namikawa
12. *Otouto Nante Ira Nai* (弟なんていらない) by Rintarou Suzawa
13. **You Stupid Onii-chan** (*Onii-chan no Baka*, お兄ちゃんのバカ) by Miki Amano
14. *Oogon no Aki* (黄金の秋) by Mai Kawamoto
15. *Hanabusa* (はなぶさ) by Maiko Watano
16. **Asteroid of Love** (*Koisuru Suisei*, 恋する彗星) by Shusaku Namikawa
As the end of the world approaches, two old acquaintances reunite for one last time...
17. *Pretty Encounter* (プリティ・エンカウンター) by Yukosa Karo
18. **Dagashi Meals for Yaegashi-san** (*Yaegashi-san no Dagashi Meshi*, 八重樫さんへの駄菓子飯) by Yoh Sakuma
Yaegashi-san is a girl with an unbalanced diet: she only eats Dagashi for lunch. One day, a classmate of hers, Takaya-kun who cooks for himself, lays eyes on her and somehow, he starts teaching her how to make meals using Dagashi...
19. *Umi no Mukou no Tooi Kuni* (海の向こうの遠い国) by Suisei Matsumoto
20. *Geranium no Niwa* (ゼラニウムの庭) by Tama Mitsuboshi

---
**Winter 2022 Contents**
1. *Hagane no Hanayome* (鋼の花嫁) by Acky Bright
2. **The World We Pretend Not to Notice** (*Shiranaifuri no Kuni*, 知らないふりの国) by Harikamo
A young boy discovers his own nature in a world only he is able to perceive.
3. *Manatsu no Sekai Seifuku* (真夏の世界征服) by Nanako Inushima
4. **Hamelin's Window** (*Hamelin no Mado*, ハーメルンの窓) by Ameishi
They say that peafowl are the mounts of the gods.
5. *Seishun no Hikage* (青春の日陰) by Asami Sekiya
6. **Our Extraordinary Days Begin Here!** (*Oretachi no Hinichijou wa Korekara da!*, 俺たちの非日常はこれからだ！) by Ohtake Masao
7. *Nijiko to Yomeiri* (ニジコと嫁入り) by Sumiko Arai
8. *Natsu to Kawa to Kimi to Ase* (夏と川と君と汗) by Yuta Konatsu
9. *Konna koto ga Attara Iinoni na* (こんなことがあったらいいのにな) by Mizoko Tsuno
10. *Slime no Tsukurikata* (スライムのつくりかた) by Corsica
11. *Douse Ashita mo Onaji Kimi* (どうせ明日も同じ君) by Iko Rota
12. *TOXiC* by Iyo Ohtsuka
13. *Meiko no Koi* (メイコの恋) by Hiro Inuzuka
14. *Sekai no Himitsu* (世界の秘密) by Shun Matsusaka
15. *Mahou Shoujo no Imouto* (魔法少女の妹) by Natsuomi Takahashi
16. *Hana ni Kurenai* (花に紅) by Rei Abe
17. *Tokage no Ryuugi* (蜥蜴の流儀) by Yoh Sakuma
18. *Otome Tsubaki no Niwa* (乙女椿の庭) by Mame Ayashiro
19. *Tsuki no Hito* (月の人) by Reika Aihama
20. *Saka no Ue no Mahoutsukai* (坂の上の魔法使い) by Kaiko Fuyumushi
21. *Watashi ga Butai Onkyou datta Koro* (私が舞台音響だった頃) by Hiraku
22. *Akai Yuuhi no Hanashi* (紅い夕陽の話) by Oku
